high_descs: Approach the counter to the right of the oven.
Pick up the the pepper shaker from the counter.
Turn to your left and and walk to the circular table.
Place the pepper shaker on the circular table.
Turn around and and walk to the counter to the right of the oven,
pick up the salt shaker from the counter.
Turn to your left and and walk to the circular table.
Place the salt shaker on the circular table.

high_descs: Take a step forward and turn to the right and walk forward to face the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the shaker on the counter.
Turn left and walk across the room then turn left to face the kitchen table.
Place the shaker on the kitchen table to the left of the cup.
Turn left and walk halfway across the room, then turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the shaker on the counter.
Turn left and walk across the room then turn left to face the kitchen table.
Place the shaker on the kitchen table to the right of the cup.

high_descs: Take two steps then turn right and walk to the counter.
Pick up the pepper grinder that's furthest from you.
Turn left and walk to the chair then turn right and walk to the fridge then turn left and take a step then turn left.
Put the pepper grinder to the left of the mug.
Go back to where you got the first pepper grinder..
Pick up the pepper grinder that's in front of you.
Go back to where you put the first pepper grinder.
Put the pepper grinder to the right of the mug.
anns.task_desc: Put two pepper grinders on the table.
